<br>
You can't mez charmed mobs in a blue server because they are considered a pet.<br>
<br>
Don't charm lv 50+ mobs or you'll just get summoned no matter how fast you run. Also, the casting time is very important to try re-charming. Without snare or root a casting time of lets say 6.0 secs would make it almost impossible to re-charm. You can be far away but spells have a maximum casting range and the mob might be on top of you before you finish casting.<br>
<br>
So, in conclusion, Mez summon=Great, even a short mez of 18.0 or 24.0 secs; charm summon=mage goo (unless you have support from another class).<br>
