<br>
Do you know of many enchanters that would run the risk of uberhasting a normal charm pet? I know of pleanty that do with Dire Charmies, but there, odds are the haste will wear off before the charm does. I'm not sure of any sane enchanter that hastes regular charmies unless they're planning on keeping some uber high level mob under their spell and are capable of dealing with it when they must recharm.<br>
